<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/9 (Sun.) The life of Queen Elizabeth II / Jab rule for outbound travelers dropped (Host: Gal)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=659&amp;p=687#p687"><![CDATA[
10/9 (Sun.) The life of Queen Elizabeth II / Jab rule for outbound travelers dropped (Host: Gal)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 1. The life of Queen Elizabeth II <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2QffVSgq9xQ">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2QffVSgq9xQ</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. Queen Elizabeth seems to eat just for health. What is your attitude for food? how to live a long and healthy life via diet?<br />2.What’s the connection between sense of humor and healthy life in your opinion?(Such as Queen Elizabeth taking out a toast during tea time with Paddington Bear)<br />3.How is your feeling about Queen Elizabeth ‘s principle &quot;never complain, never explain&quot; while facing dirty linen.<br />4. Queen Elizabeth loves walking her pets and riding horse so much that these habits bring her a pair of healthy and strong legs. Do you have this kind of habit to strengthen your body? <br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 2. Jab rule for outbound travelers dropped<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2022/10/03/2003786347">https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan ... 2003786347</a><!-- m --><br /> <br />Questions:<br />1.Do you know what is the situation abroad now? Japan? Europe? USA? Thailand?<br />2.Will you or your friends plan to travel abroad after 13, Oct?<br />3.Did you or your friends go abroad during the pandemic these 3 years?<br />4.How to balance or adjust our mind to travel abroad at post-pandemic era?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Tue Oct 04, 2022 7:36 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
